<div class="panel-body list-group collapse out" data-propname="FollowUpCare" id="article-FollowUpCare" role="tabpanel" style="display: none;">
<h2>Long-term outcomes</h2>
<p>Treatment outcomes are different for everyone with amblyopia. Outcomes depend on the cause of amblyopia and the age of the patient when they are treated. Following treatment instructions and attending follow-up visits is important to know how a patient’s vision is responding to their treatment and so your child’s health-care provider can adjust treatment as needed.</p> </div>
</div>
